their hands on you.

00:57.753 --> 01:00.756
"Human Rights Violations by the
CIA" has its own Wikipedia page.

01:00.799 --> 01:03.889
You know, if bad guys jumped
out from behind a bush,

01:03.933 --> 01:06.109
I got our trusty guard dog here
to protect us.

01:06.153 --> 01:07.980
Yeah. Fenway's afraid
of marshmallows.

01:08.024 --> 01:11.549
I don't think she'd be much help
with CIA commandos.

01:11.593 --> 01:15.423
You know, six weeks ago,
if the Feds had

01:15.466 --> 01:17.599
wanted to throw me off
the roof of that building,

01:17.642 --> 01:19.688
you would've run across
the street to grab a ladder.

01:19.731 --> 01:21.733
What can I say,
you've grown on me,

01:21.777 --> 01:23.822
like a barnacle or a fungus.

01:23.866 --> 01:25.563
Just be careful, okay?

01:25.607 --> 01:26.956
I will.

01:29.045 --> 01:31.526
Really, Fenway?

01:31.569 --> 01:32.918
Marshmallows?

01:34.572 --> 01:36.661
AJ:
The flood may be over, but
