02:59.091 --> 03:01.311
To root for the
Lakers? Come on, AJ.

03:01.355 --> 03:02.965
All right, you three.
It's time for lunch.

03:03.008 --> 03:04.314
It's Milkshake Monday.

03:04.358 --> 03:05.968
Oh, Milkshake Monday?

03:06.011 --> 03:07.622
You sure are getting
spoiled, Dad.

03:07.665 --> 03:10.451
Not for much longer.

03:10.494 --> 03:13.236
Rumor is MediCo
is trying to buy this place.

03:13.280 --> 03:14.542
What's MediCo?

03:14.585 --> 03:15.804
