03:15.847 --> 03:18.285
They buy up hospitals,
then they cut costs

03:18.328 --> 03:19.634
and jack up
the prices.

03:19.677 --> 03:21.026
It's disgraceful.

03:21.070 --> 03:22.376
I-I'm on a budget, Gloria.

03:22.419 --> 03:24.160
What happens if, you know,

03:24.204 --> 03:25.335
if I can't cover the new rates?

03:25.379 --> 03:26.554
[exhales]
Don't ask me.

03:26.597 --> 03:29.296
I do milkshakes,
not balance sheets.

03:33.474 --> 03:34.779
Thank you all
for staying so focused

03:34.823 --> 03:36.390
during the flood repairs.

03:36.433 --> 03:38.392
Everything should be dried out
in the next few weeks.

03:38.435 --> 03:40.698
